data.description: Welcome Home! OFFERING $5,000 CREDIT TO BUYER. NEW ROOF Complete. Ease into your mortgage with a FREE temporary rate buy down when using the preferred lender. The preferred lender will pay for a 1-0 buydown which reduces your rate by 1% in year one.  Enjoy this spacious open floor plan and new screened in porch. Sit and relax on the back porch overlooking the woods. A convenient separate laundry room is also located on the first floor. Upstairs are two spacious main bedrooms. Each bedroom has its own en- suite bathroom, walk-in closet, and ceiling fans. One of the bathrooms has a double vanity.
